href=\"https://svelte.dev/docs#svelte_store\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Svelte Store</a>, which returns <code>true</code> whenever <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/matchMedia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><code>matchMedia(SCHEME)</code></a> is validated.</p>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: Change your Operating System's color settings to see changes.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<pre class=\"highlight language-svelte\" data-identifier=\"prefersscheme-preview\" data-mode=\"repl\" data-syntax=\"svelte\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        Code<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        Heading<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        Text<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        prefersscheme<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> darkmode_store <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">prefersscheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"dark\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> lightmode_store <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">prefersscheme</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"light\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Heading</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>User Color Scheme Preferences<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Heading</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    Darkmode: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>$darkmode_store<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    Lightmode: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>$lightmode_store<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"t